response: 1 Million Women To Tech is a 501(c)3 not-for-profit community organization in the Silicon Valley dedicated to empowering women, companies, and societies and fueling the rise of the digital economy, by providing technical education to women. 1 Million Women To Tech are partnering with Oxford Entrepreneurs , Europe’s largest student startup society drawing members from all parts of Oxford University for the program.
